Vision Statement It is Davidson Green Center’s vision to build community by bringing children, families, and other Davidson residents together in discovering nature and inspired life-long learning. The Davidson Green Center will meet this two-pronged mission by providing a school, afterschool programs, and camps that specifically give children opportunities to build and use the focus skills, as well as providing the indoor and outdoor facilities to the wider community.
